sources.title: Choke Canyon 1986 (Action, Sci-Fi, Western film) directed by Charles Bail
sources.description:
A "cowboy"-scientist is fighting a corporation who wants to dump atomic waste on a piece of land he has leased.

Original title: Choke Canyon 1986

This film is available with subtitles in many language options.


Director: Charles Bail
Writers: Sheila Goldberg, Ovidio G. Assonitis, Alfonso Brescia
Stars: Stephen Collins, Janet Julian, Bo Svenson
Genres: Action, Sci-Fi, Western
Budget: $7,000,000 (estimated)
